----------------------------------
Crowd Counting Demo Application
----------------------------------

* Deep learning application for head detection, counting and generating heatmap based on the detected heads.

----------------------------------
Steps to run the demo application	
----------------------------------

* Clone the repository,
	* git clone https://github.com/dilipkumar25/smartecam-ai-samples.git

* Change directory to repository directory,
	* cd smartecam-ai-samples

* Create directory structure,
	* mkdir -p /opt/econ/dlapp

* Copy the application into SmarteCam device,
	* sudo cp -r crowd_counting/* /opt/econ/dlapp

* Download the model file from google drive, 
	* https://drive.google.com/file/d/1F4CJy7sE6UnTQepSHJt9aIlA5P_Hi-8f/view?usp=sharing

* Create directory,
	* sudo mkdir -p /opt/econ/dlapp/dlapp/econ/peopletracking/models/

* Copy the model file to the models location,
	* sudo cp trt_nofpn_crowd_v1.pb /opt/econ/dlapp/dlapp/econ/peopletracking/models/

* Run the application using the command,
	* /opt/econ/dlapp/crowd_demo

